  "description": "Professional fruit agronomist and plant pathologist specializing in fruit crop diagnosis, disease identification, and orchard management. Provides expert guidance on mango, avocado, pawpaw, apple, citrus, passion fruit, banana, guava, grapes, strawberry, and pineapple cultivation with focus on East African farming contexts.",
